'use strict'
import 'antd/dist/antd.css'; 
import '@shopify/polaris/styles.css'
import dynamic from 'next/dynamic'
const AppProviderDynamic = dynamic(() =>
  Promise.resolve(require('@shopify/polaris').AppProvider)
)
import { Page, Form, ContextualSaveBar,TextField, Card  } from "@shopify/polaris";
import {  Row, Col } from "antd";


export default class Mocker extends React.Component{


    render () {
        return (
       <AppProviderDynamic>
<Page fullWidth>
<ContextualSaveBar
        message="Unsaved changes"
        saveAction={{
          onAction: () => console.log('add form submit logic'),
          loading: false,
          disabled: false,
        }}
        discardAction={{
          onAction: () => console.log('add clear form logic'),
        }}
      />

<Row>

          <Col lg={12}>

          <Card sectioned title="Add new mock endpoint">
          <TextField
        label="Endpoint"
        type="number"
        prefix="https://demoaccount.com/"
      />
        <TextField
        label="Price"
        type="number"
        prefix="$"
      />
          </Card>
     
          </Col>

          <Col lg={11} offset={1}>

<Card sectioned>
<TextField
label="Endpoint"
type="number"
prefix="https://demoaccount.com/"
/>
<TextField
label="Price"
type="number"
prefix="$"
/>
</Card>

</Col>
         </Row>


</Page>

       </AppProviderDynamic> 
        )
    }
}
